<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 10px; text-align: left;">Welcome to the first issue of Direct from the Sun, a monthly newsletter from Direct Energy Solar. We&rsquo;re excited to bring you the latest solar highlights, exclusive resources, and helpful advice for going solar. In addition to our monthly newsletter, we invite you to continue browsing and learning more about solar (and us!) at <a style="text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; color: #61af3f;" href="http://directenergysolar.com?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_source=febnews&amp;utm_campaign=nurture-tk&amp;utm_content=febnews-link-learn">Directenergysolar.com</a>.</p>
